title: Converse Wall to Wall Series: Huntington Beach with Artist Push
description:
Artist Push took his geometric stylings to the side of the Livery Gruppe building in Huntington Beach this summer, creating an epic piece of beach side art. 

For more on the Converse Wall to Wall series: http://wwwconverse.com/WalltoWall
